}}\n|-\n!18\n|align=\"center\"|18\n|{{flagicon|CAN}} [[Lance Stroll]] \n|[[Williams Grand Prix Engineering|Williams]]-[[Mercedes AMG High Performance Powertrains|Mercedes]]\n|1:10.776\n|\n|\n|align=\"center\"|16{{ref|4|4}}\n|-\n!19\n|align=\"center\"|9\n|{{flagicon|SWE}} [[Marcus Ericsson]] \n|[[Sauber]]-[[Scuderia Ferrari|Ferrari]]\n|1:10.875\n|\n|\n|align=\"center\"|17{{ref|5|5}}\n|-\n!colspan=\"8\"|[[107% rule|107% time]]: 1:14.263\n|-\n!\u2014\n|align=\"center\"|44\n|{{flagicon|GBR}} [[Lewis Hamilton]] \n|[[Mercedes-Benz in Formula One|Mercedes]]\n|No time\n|\n|\n|align=\"center\"|PL{{ref|6|6}}\n|-\n!colspan=\"8\"|Source:<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.fia.com/file/63343/download?token=4OHMr_kA |title=2017 Brazilian Grand Prix \u2013 Qualifying Session Official Classification |date=11 November 2017 |publisher=[[FIA]] |accessdate=18 November 2017 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171118170953/https://www.fia.com/file/63343/download?token=4OHMr_kA |archive-date=18 November 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.fia.com/file/63350/download?token=UNV0ufsG |title=2017 Brazilian Grand Prix \u2013 Official Starting Grid |date=12 November 2017 |publisher=[[FIA]] |accessdate=18 November 2017 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171118171334/https://www.fia.com/file/63350/download?token=UNV0ufsG |archive-date=18 November 2017}}</ref>\n|}\n;Notes\n*{{note|1|1}}&nbsp;\u2013 [[Daniel Ricciardo]] received a 10-place grid penalty for exceeding his quota of power unit components.\n*{{note|2|2}}&nbsp;\u2013 [[Brendon Hartley]] received a 10-place grid penalty for exceeding his quota of power unit components.\n*{{note|3|3}}&nbsp;\u2013 [[Pierre Gasly]] received a 25-place grid penalty for exceeding his quota of power unit components.\n*{{note|4|4}}&nbsp;\u2013 [[Lance Stroll]] received a 5-place grid penalty for an unscheduled gearbox change. \n*{{note|5|5}}&nbsp;\u2013 [[Marcus Ericsson]] received a 5-place grid penalty for an unscheduled gearbox change. \n*{{note|6|6}}&nbsp;\u2013 [[Lewis Hamilton]] failed to set a time within the 107% requirement, but received permission from the stewards to start the race. He also started from the pit lane due to a gearbox and power unit changes.\n\n===Race===\n{|class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size: 85%;\"\n!{{Tooltip|Pos.|Position}}\n!{{Tooltip|No.|Car number}}\n!Driver\n!Constructor\n!Laps\n!Time/Retired\n!Grid\n!Points\n|-\n!1\n|align=\"center\"|5\n|{{flagicon|GER}} '''[[Sebastian Vettel]]''' \n|'''[[Scuderia Ferrari|Ferrari]]'''\n|71\n| 1:31:26.262\n|2\n|align=\"center\"|'''25'''\n|-\n!2\n|align=\"center\"|77\n|{{flagicon|FIN}} '''[[Valtteri Bottas]]''' \n|'''[[Mercedes-Benz in Formula One|Mercedes]]'''\n|71\n| +2.762\n|1\n|align=\"center\"|'''18'''\n|-\n!3\n|align=\"center\"|7\n|{{flagicon|FIN}} '''[[Kimi R\u00e4ikk\u00f6nen]]''' \n|'''[[Scuderia Ferrari|Ferrari]]'''\n|71\n| +4.600\n|3\n|align=\"center\"|'''15'''\n|-\n!4\n|align=\"center\"|44\n|{{flagicon|GBR}} '''[[Lewis Hamilton]]''' \n|'''[[Mercedes-Benz in Formula One|Mercedes]]'''\n|71\n| +5.468\n|PL\n|align=\"center\"|'''12'''\n|-\n!5\n|align=\"center\"|33\n|{{flagicon|NED}} '''[[Max Verstappen]]''' \n|'''{{nowrap|[[Red Bull Racing]]-[[TAG Heuer]]}}'''\n|71\n| +32.940\n|4\n|align=\"center\"|'''10'''\n|-\n!6\n|align=\"center\"|3\n|{{flagicon|AUS}} '''[[Daniel Ricciardo]]'''\n|'''{{nowrap|[[Red Bull Racing]]-[[TAG Heuer]]}}'''\n|71\n| +48.691\n|14\n|align=\"center\"| '''8'''\n|-\n!7\n|align=\"center\"|19\n|{{flagicon|BRA}} '''[[Felipe Massa]]'''\n|'''[[Williams Grand Prix Engineering|Williams]]-[[Mercedes AMG High Performance Powertrains|Mercedes]]'''\n|71\n| +1:08.882\n|9\n|align=\"center\"| '''6'''\n|-\n!8\n|align=\"center\"|14\n|{{flagicon|ESP}} '''[[Fernando Alonso]]''' \n|'''[[McLaren]]-[[Honda in Formula One|Honda]]'''\n|71\n| +1:09.363\n|6\n|align=\"center\"|'''4'''\n|-\n!9\n|align=\"center\"|11\n|{{flagicon|MEX}} '''[[Sergio P\u00e9rez]]''' \n|'''[[Force India]]-[[Mercedes AMG High Performance Powertrains|Mercedes]]'''\n|71\n| +1:09.500\n|5\n|align=\"center\"|'''2'''\n|-\n!10\n|align=\"center\"|27\n|'''{{flagicon|GER}} [[Nico H\u00fclkenberg]]'''\n|'''[[Renault in Formula One|Renault]]'''\n|70\n| +1 Lap\n|7\n|align=\"center\"|'''1'''\n|-\n!11\n|align=\"center\"|55\n|{{flagicon|ESP}} [[Carlos Sainz Jr.]]\n|[[Renault in Formula One|Renault]]\n|70\n| +1 Lap\n|8\n|align=\"center\"|\n|-\n!12\n|align=\"center\"|10\n|{{flagicon|FRA}} [[Pierre Gasly]] \n|[[Scuderia Toro Rosso|Toro Rosso]]\n|70\n| +1 Lap\n|19\n|align=\"center\"|\n|-\n!13\n|align=\"center\"|9\n|{{flagicon|SWE}} [[Marcus Ericsson]] \n|[[Sauber]]-[[Scuderia Ferrari|Ferrari]]\n|70\n| +1 Lap\n|17\n|\n|-\n!14\n|align=\"center\"|94\n|{{flagicon|GER}} [[Pascal Wehrlein]] \n|[[Sauber]]-[[Scuderia Ferrari|Ferrari]]\n|70\n| +1 Lap\n|15\n|align=\"center\"|\n|-\n!15\n|align=\"center\"|8\n|{{flagicon|FRA}} [[Romain Grosjean]] \n|[[Haas F1 Team|Haas]]-[[Scuderia Ferrari|Ferrari]]\n|69\n| +2 Laps\n|11\n|align=\"center\"|\n|-\n!16\n|align=\"center\"|18\n|{{flagicon|CAN}} [[Lance Stroll]]\n|[[Williams Grand Prix Engineering|Williams]]-[[Mercedes AMG High Performance Powertrains|Mercedes]]\n|69\n| +2 Laps\n|16\n|\n|-\n!Ret\n|align=\"center\"|28\n|{{flagicon|NZL}} [[Brendon Hartley]] \n|[[Scuderia Toro Rosso|Toro Rosso]]\n|40\n|Engine\n|18\n|\n|-\n!Ret\n|align=\"center\"|31\n|{{flagicon|FRA}} [[Esteban Ocon]]\n|[[Force India]]-[[Mercedes AMG High Performance Powertrains|Mercedes]]\n|0\n|Collision\n|10\n|\n|-\n!Ret\n|align=\"center\"|2\n|{{nowrap|{{flagicon|BEL}} [[Stoffel Vandoorne]]}}\n|[[McLaren]]-[[Honda in Formula One|Honda]]\n|0\n|Collision\n|12\n|align=\"center\"|\n|-\n!Ret\n|align=\"center\"|20\n|{{nowrap|{{flagicon|DEN}} [[Kevin Magnussen]]}}\n|[[Haas F1 Team|Haas]]-[[Scuderia Ferrari|Ferrari]]\n|0\n|Collision\n|13\n|\n|-\n!colspan=\"8\"|Source:<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.fia.com/file/63369/download?token=PDNoC_B1 |title=2017 Brazilian Grand Prix \u2013 Race Official Classification |date=12 November 2017 |publisher=[[FIA]] |accessdate=18 November 2017 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171118170445/https://www.fia.com/file/63369/download?token=PDNoC_B1 |archive-date=18 November 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n|}\n\n===Championship standings after the race===\n{{col-start}}\n{{col-2}}\n;Drivers' Championship standings\n{|class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size: 85%;\"\n|-\n!\n!{{Tooltip|Pos.|Position}}\n!Driver\n!Points\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|[[File:1rightarrow blue.svg|10px]]\n|align=\"center\"|1\n|{{flagicon|GBR}} [[Lewis Hamilton]]\n|align=\"left\"|345\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|[[File:1rightarrow blue.svg|10px]]\n|align=\"center\"|2\n|{{flagicon|GER}} [[Sebastian Vettel]]\n|align=\"left\"|302\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|[[File:1rightarrow blue.svg|10px]]\n|align=\"center\"|3\n|{{flagicon|FIN}} [[Valtteri Bottas]]\n|align=\"left\"|280\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|[[File:1rightarrow blue.svg|10px]]\n|align=\"center\"|4\n|{{flagicon|AUS}} [[Daniel Ricciardo]]\n|align=\"left\"|200\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|[[File:1rightarrow blue.svg|10px]]\n|align=\"center\"|5\n|{{flagicon|FIN}} [[Kimi R\u00e4ikk\u00f6nen]]\n|align=\"left\"|193\n|-\n!colspan=4|Source:<ref name=\"champ\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.statsf1.com/en/2017/bresil/championnat.aspx|title=Brazil 2017 - Championship \u2022 STATS F1|website=www.statsf1.com|access-date=13 March 2019}}</ref>\n|}\n{{col-2}}\n;Constructors' Championship standings\n{|class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size: 85%;\"\n|-\n!\n!{{Tooltip|Pos.|Position}}\n!Constructor\n!Points\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|[[File:1rightarrow blue.svg|10px]]\n|align=\"center\"|1\n|{{flagicon|GER}} [[Mercedes-Benz in Formula One|Mercedes]]\n|align=\"left\"|625\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|[[File:1rightarrow blue.svg|10px]]\n|align=\"center\"|2\n|{{flagicon|ITA}} [[Scuderia Ferrari|Ferrari]]\n|align=\"left\"|495\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|[[File:1rightarrow blue.svg|10px]]\n|align=\"center\"|3\n|{{flagicon|AUT}} {{nowrap|[[Red Bull Racing]]-[[TAG Heuer]]}}\n|align=\"left\"|358\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|[[File:1rightarrow blue.svg|10px]]\n|a